544
00:49:32,730 --> 00:49:34,430
That's how my mom is pursuing you.

545
00:49:34,430 --> 00:49:37,640
Give her a call sometimes. I think she's sulking.

546
00:49:37,640 --> 00:49:39,910
Please tell her I said thank you.

547
00:49:39,910 --> 00:49:41,180
Sure!

548
00:49:41,180 --> 00:49:44,330
- Don't forget to say it!
- All right!

549
00:49:48,230 --> 00:49:50,220
Did he hear it?

550
00:49:51,060 --> 00:49:53,160
He must have heard it.

551
00:49:53,160 --> 00:49:55,550
Of course, he would have heard everything.

552
00:49:55,550 --> 00:49:57,620
It's embarrassing!

553
00:49:57,620 --> 00:50:00,240
What should I do?

554
00:50:00,240 --> 00:50:02,340
It's mortifying!

555
00:50:13,190 --> 00:50:15,960
My goodness, it's embarrassing.

556
00:50:31,100 --> 00:50:35,760
That's right. There's nothing more to lose.

557
00:50:35,760 --> 00:50:40,110
Let's live to the fullest and not regret anything.

558
00:50:41,250 --> 00:50:43,850
I can do it!

559
00:50:46,070 --> 00:50:48,210
I can do it.

