569
00:51:43,420 --> 00:51:45,040
The water pipe is broken.

570
00:51:45,040 --> 00:51:47,970
I definitely told you before, fix everything on your own.

571
00:51:47,970 --> 00:51:49,720
- You slept in the library before.
